{"tid":2224994,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［支那國民教育］教育局又出洗腦文宣！","createTime":"2020-10-01T03:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T11:01:04.000Z","uid":234894,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"29476371e67d06535e9400bd61a77893942a685a","tid":2224994,"uid":234894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T03:42:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/kla/pshe/basic-law-education/cble_wallcharts/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcurriculum-development%2Fkla%2Fpshe%2Fbasic-law-education%2Fcble_wallcharts%2Findex.html&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=b74d0a37\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/kla/pshe/basic-law-education/cble_wallcharts/index.html</a><br />\n冇耐之前教育局嘅網頁出咗一份「基本法教材」，呢份所謂嘅基本法教材入面就講話香港同澳門比聯合國踢出咗殖民地名單，所以冇自決權利，仲要強調「香港獨立」喺國際法上面冇任何合理依據。<br />\n<br />\n但係其實呢樣嘢並唔係事實，只不過係教育局隱瞞部份事實避重就輕，希望藉此洗腦下一代。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ot0ta1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fot0ta1F.jpg&h=47f5fed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r0ynftq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr0ynftq.jpg&h=f3cb5fa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然之後有手足立即出咗相關嘅文宣反駁教育局嘅戇鳩文宣，大家幫幫手廣傳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MNxvpob.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMNxvpob.jpg&h=371aadf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5HbcCJe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5HbcCJe.jpg&h=3620458c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d4bzQ3i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd4bzQ3i.jpg&h=51256142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aD4tVu1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaD4tVu1.jpg&h=27d52ec6